{
  "texts": [
    "All the images are resized to 224 × 224.",
    "Typical data augmentations including random width/height shift, color jittering and random horizontal flip are applied.For Animal-10N dataset, we follow the experimental setting in previous works [27].",
    "We use VGG-19 with batch normalization.",
    "The SGD optimizer is employed.",
    "We train the network for 100 epochs and use an initial learning rate of 0.1, which is divided by 5 at 50% and 75% of the total number of epochs."
  ]
}